'''华为Mate Xs'''是[[华为|华为]]公司于2020年2月24日发布的[[可摺疊式智能手機|折叠式智能手机]]，折叠形态为横向外折。

Mate Xs较其前代[[华为Mate_X|华为Mate X]]在外观上没有大的变动，但其SoC更换成了集成[[5G|5G]]的麒麟990 5G。

==设计==
由于Mate X仅在国内市场发行，面向国际市场的华为Mate Xs在外观上并未较大幅度更动<ref>{{cite web |title=Huawei Mate XS review: Know when to hold 'em and when to fold 'em |url=https://www.androidauthority.com/huawei-mate-xs-review-1086018/ |website=Android Authority |accessdate=2020-11-07 |date=2020-08-19 |archive-date=2020-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207065703/https://www.androidauthority.com/huawei-mate-xs-review-1086018/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

Mate Xs采用外翻式折叠屏，展开后右手一端有便于手持的凸起，四枚摄像头亦排布在这一条凸起上<ref>{{cite web |author1=Andy Boxall |title=Huawei Mate Xs folding phone review: Flawed marvel |url=https://www.digitaltrends.com/cell-phone-reviews/huawei-mate-xs-review/ |website=www.digitaltrends.com |accessdate=2020-11-07 |archive-date=2020-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211075905/https://www.digitaltrends.com/cell-phone-reviews/huawei-mate-xs-review/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。折叠铰链处采用华为自研“鹰翼式”铰链<ref name="#1">{{cite web |title=HUAWEI Mate Xs - 华为官网 |url=https://consumer.huawei.com/cn/phones/mate-x-s/ |website=consumer.huawei.com |accessdate=2020-11-08 |language=zh-CN |archive-date=2020-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928235122/https://consumer.huawei.com/cn/phones/mate-x-s/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，该铰链是华为Mate X上铰链的升级版<ref>{{cite web |last1=March 2020 |first1=Abbas Jaffar Ali 26 |title=Huawei Mate Xs review |url=https://www.techradar.com/reviews/huawei-mate-xs |website=TechRadar |accessdate=2020-11-08 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129150526/https://www.techradar.com/reviews/huawei-mate-xs |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Mate Xs只有“星际蓝”一种配色。

Mate Xs采用了[[京东方|京东方]]的8英寸柔性OLED屏幕<ref>{{cite web |title=Huawei says it lost $60 million on its Mate Xs foldable smartphone in two months {{!}} OLED-Info |url=https://www.oled-info.com/huawei-says-it-lost-60-million-its-foldable-mate-xs-two-months |website=www.oled-info.com |accessdate=2020-11-08 |archive-date=2021-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418051020/https://www.oled-info.com/huawei-says-it-lost-60-million-its-foldable-mate-xs-two-months }}</ref>，华为消费者业务CEO[[余承东|余承东]]表示，Mate Xs所用的折叠屏价格不菲，华为在Mate Xs发布前已经投入了超过6000-7000万美元在Mate Xs的研发和生产上<ref>{{cite web |title=Huawei says it lost over $60 million on the Mate Xs foldable phone |url=https://www.gsmarena.com/huawei_says_its_lost_over_60_million_on_the_mate_xs_foldable_phone-news-42550.php |website=GSMArena.com |accessdate=2020-11-08 |archive-date=2020-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200529154657/https://www.gsmarena.com/huawei_says_its_lost_over_60_million_on_the_mate_xs_foldable_phone-news-42550.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而在Mate Xs发布前，中国股市屏幕面板板块大幅上涨<ref>{{cite web |title=今天市场一大热点！华为将推折叠屏手机，概念股集体大涨-新闻-上海证券报·中国证券网 |url=http://news.cnstock.com/news,bwkx-202002-4492561.htm |website=news.cnstock.com |accessdate=2020-11-08 |archive-date=2020-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810075311/http://news.cnstock.com/news,bwkx-202002-4492561.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==性能及体验==
华为Mate Xs搭载[[海思|海思麒麟990 5G]] SoC芯片<ref>{{cite web |title=Huawei Mate Xs launched with improved hinge design and Kirin 990 5G SoC |url=https://pocketnow.com/huawei-mate-xs-launched-with-improved-hinge-design-and-kirin-990-5g-soc |website=Pocketnow |accessdate=2020-11-08 |date=2020-02-24 |archive-date=2020-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200618132930/https://pocketnow.com/huawei-mate-xs-launched-with-improved-hinge-design-and-kirin-990-5g-soc |dead-url=no }}</ref>，该芯片亦在[[华为Mate_30系列|华为Mate 30系列]]、[[华为P40|华为P40系列]]等华为旗舰手机上被搭载。其基于[[台灣積體電路製造|台积电]]7nm+ EUV工艺制作，是第一款基于该工艺制作的SoC芯片<ref>{{cite web |title=Kirin 990 To Be the First Customer to Use a TSMC Process Using EUV |url=https://www.gizchina.com/2018/12/27/kirin-990-tsmc-euv/ |website=Gizchina.com |accessdate=2020-11-08 |date=2018-12-27 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108115417/https://www.gizchina.com/2018/12/27/kirin-990-tsmc-euv/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，内置巴龙5000 5G基带<ref>{{cite web |title=HUAWEI Kirin 990 Series, Rethink Evolution {{!}} HUAWEI Global |url=https://consumer.huawei.com/en/campaign/kirin-990-series/ |website=consumer.huawei.com |accessdate=2020-11-08 |archive-date=2020-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929222002/https://consumer.huawei.com/en/campaign/kirin-990-series/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，搭载基于[[ARM_Cortex-A76|ARM Cortex-A76]]和[[ARM_Cortex-A55|ARM Cortex-A55]]的8核CPU以及16核[[Mali_(GPU)|Mali G76]] GPU<ref>{{cite web |last1=Sohail |first1=Omar |title=Huawei Kirin 990 Is Official - Integrated 5G With 7nm+ EUV Node, 10.3 Billion Transistors, 16-Core GPU & More |url=https://wccftech.com/huawei-kirin-990-official-5g-modem-7nm-euv-specs-features/ |website=Wccftech |accessdate=2020-11-08 |date=2019-09-06 |archive-date=2020-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106211034/https://wccftech.com/huawei-kirin-990-official-5g-modem-7nm-euv-specs-features/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

Mate Xs的指纹识别器与电源键合一，被放置在手持凸起一侧<ref>{{cite web |title=Huawei's Mate Xs is a terrific foldable phone, without Google Services |url=https://www.nextpit.com/huawei-mate-xs-review |website=NextPit |accessdate=2020-11-08 |language=en |archive-date=2020-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021021719/https://www.nextpit.com/huawei-mate-xs-review |dead-url=no }}</ref>。散热方面，Mate Xs使用自研“飞鱼鳍散热”系统<ref name="#1"/>，据[[IFixit|IFixit]]和中国大陆“艾奥科技”的拆解情况，除了该使用“仿生柔性石墨”的散热系统，Mate Xs在主板下亦有铜管散热装置<ref>{{cite web |author1=Andy Yang |title=华为 Mate Xs 视频拆解，胶水用得出乎意外的少 |url=https://cn.engadget.com/cn-2020-03-12-huawei-mate-xs-teardown.html?guccounter=1&guce_referrer=aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbS8&guce_referrer_sig=AQAAALvu_WcDxUn4pLK8MTxt0auO6S-n66PwMQMtl1GwI_XSYJRH_p7_qwVcHZzTOj5zLgk_glUBt73c39NDGhQgJ6BVrV_zgMQ1MYa0NbsfXP6uyX8QvcGYVDqFDGO7DF3BR390eZHt5tSIvJTZTQa2q_UgwQwHgYqniVky4KoQZTYG |website=Engadget 中国版 |accessdate=2020-11-08}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Donnell |first1=Deirdre O. |title=iFixit's Huawei Mate Xs teardown does little for the foldable category's reputation for durability |url=https://www.notebookcheck.net/iFixit-s-Huawei-Mate-Xs-teardown-does-little-for-the-foldable-category-s-reputation-for-durability.461035.0.html |website=Notebookcheck |accessdate=2020-11-08 |language=en |archive-date=2020-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610092508/https://www.notebookcheck.net/iFixit-s-Huawei-Mate-Xs-teardown-does-little-for-the-foldable-category-s-reputation-for-durability.461035.0.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

华为Mate Xs搭载4500毫安时电池，支持55W快充<ref>{{cite web |title=Huawei Mate XS |url=https://www.phonefoldable.com/product/huawei-mate-xs/ |website=Foldable Phone Online Shopping |accessdate=2020-11-08 |date=2020-02-10 |archive-date=2020-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113161225/https://www.phonefoldable.com/product/huawei-mate-xs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
